flare - distributed, and persistent key-value storage
------------------------

* you can find documentation here:

https://github.com/gree/flare/wiki (English)
https://github.com/gree/flare/wiki/Home-JP (Japanese)

* thanks to Tokyo Cabinet (http://fallabs.com/tokyocabinet/)

* notes on flarefs
  * no hard link supported
  * no sym link supoprted
  * no atime supported
  * return EACCES instead of ENOATTR on *xattr();
